I tried 3 apps to extract EDID information from
a Proview 20" LCD monitor in WinXP.

-  NirSoft MonitorInfoView 1.02
    http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/monitor_info_view.html

-  Phoenix EDID Designer 1.3  downloaded from
    http://www.tucows.com/preview/329441

-  EnTech Taiwan softMCCS 2.11  downloaded from
    http://www.tucows.com/preview/329441

The last one (softMCCS) gave me the most complete information.

Regards,

Anton.


